Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}3米2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}西村同学 芹泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐呐 说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你跟长谷同学到底是什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么会提到长谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看你这个反应 果然是有些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直都很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}午休时间两人都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说真的 到底怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学是非常重要的朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 真纯情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐呐 什么时候开始变得要好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从五月左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一开始是长谷同学主动来找你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是怎么说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个记得很清楚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他跟我说了「请跟我做朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学也好纯情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}纯情？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学给人的印象就是很善良呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 非常善良的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拒人于千里之外的藤宫同学敞开了心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是那个意思了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么他是有多善良呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之就是非常温柔 对我很贴心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是个十分值得信赖的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我真的很高兴能够跟长谷同学相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 听完连我也开始心跳加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后呢 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}轮到沙希了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要上了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}38厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}新纪录～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乖乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说起来你跟桐生同学也是朋友对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听沙希说你们之前还办了学习会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}桐生同学不错喔 虽然我觉得长谷同学也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我算是桐生同学那派的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那种不合群的性格真是太棒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这家伙水平比较低 不要在意喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沙希也觉得桐生同学很帅对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是谁去了 那两个男生中的一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀呀沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是健忘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}舞子你太宠沙希了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁叫她这么小巧可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们三个真要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学不也是我们的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沙希的朋友就是我们的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要不要也叫你香织呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 香织怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 香织害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好兴奋的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发生了这样的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的朋友又变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小蓝非常可靠 是三人中的主导者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}舞子非常活泼 跟她在一起很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关于记忆的事跟他们说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有大概地说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但好像被当成是跟沙希一样的小糊涂虫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然要写进日记的事情变多了 有点慌忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但真是好开心啊
Comment: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今后日记里面 关于其他人的内容也会渐渐增多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天放学后能帮我做期末考试的备考吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那沙希也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果可以请一对一来教我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太棒了 学习喽 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}首先挑战一下这道题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以看教科书和笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是这种气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出…出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全把我当电灯泡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁叫你老是很自然地站在那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是你让我陪着你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然是这样但不是说这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别管了过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也有那个… 想静下来说话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你小子偶尔让我们两人独处一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真心话完全暴露出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之今天不需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那家伙真是只顾自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然估计会被他原句奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}班上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}名字记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就体谅你尝试去想起来的精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才在走廊里井上老师托我做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请再告诉我你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}桐生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}桐生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本人都这么说了不会有错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那请把名告诉我 这个可能更好记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正你记不住 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}桐生同学 总感觉能想起点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学是不是无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直都是长谷同学在支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有什么我能帮上忙 请让我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以不懂的地方尽管问喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前就喜欢数学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小学的算数也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是开始努力学习是从高年级开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃… 我记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记忆有点模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那喜欢的数字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一下子有点说不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}应该是喜欢「1」这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是藤宫同学成绩好不仅限于数学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有这种事 一般般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又能干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是无可挑剔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可爱是说 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么说呢 客观来说会这么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自从分到一个班里就一直觉得你很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一次被男生说可爱 吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很开心 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说山岸同学什么时候开始在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听到我们说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从你们开始讨论可不可爱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老师拜托我把这个贴上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看上去很困难 帮我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以这个人借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请贴在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里 这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再上面一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再上面 再来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差点失去平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}摔下来我可接不住你
Comment: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘴上这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好危险 好危险 山岸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 要摔下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说 山岸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沙希在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 在这在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 你们两个怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是说放学后在图书室集合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀呀 长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还真是被随意使唤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是很好使唤啊 这位男生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山岸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要去图书室的话 你去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后面就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不愧是长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那香织 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:12:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还去图书室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ho
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ho？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}…Ho？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fn腾祥铚谦钢笔简\blur0\bord0\c&H353639&}#7「Hu-」的朋友。
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马上就暑假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马上就暑假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暑假里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我说想每星期至少见一次面的话 你会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是啥 好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 藤宫同学那边可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 难得的长假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}光是有两星期的空当就够担心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从另一种意义上来说也是个不错的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暑假里故意不见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后暑假结束之后久违的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到时候来看看她还记不记得你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是完全不记得了你要怎么赔我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要信任藤宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}问题不在这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就和本人商量一下不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学完全没放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总觉得如果像往常一样期待着暑假的到来会有点不合适…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我之前就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真的好娘炮耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想让努力都成了泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是了是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}单纯只是因为暑假里见不到藤宫会感到寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说 为什么你总是向着坏的方向想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是和藤宫成为朋友以来第一个暑假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不应该像现充一样有很多快乐的活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你觉得我这种人能去邀请她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我应该邀请她去哪玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且啊 不管邀请她去哪玩 看起来都像情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对方是藤宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得不管邀请她去哪玩 她都会很高兴地跟你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}海边啊 泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烟花大会之类的 还会嫌少吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好 越来越期待暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐 藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马上就暑假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每年都很期待放暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每年暑假爸爸都会带我去旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今年会去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学暑假有什么计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没什么计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有去过国外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我呀 有去过几次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈？ 没说关于暑假的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是 好几次都想说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总是找不到好的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那怎么办啊 她没手机的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万不得已的时候 去拜访下藤宫家也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得你没这勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有点行动力的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到现在还没把想说的话说出来的你？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是真有行动力的话 现在就去跟她说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正藤宫现在肯定还在这附近走着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跑的话还能赶上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想少为你操点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真对不起 这人情我一定会还的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们暑假也见见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了啊 这么一本正经
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是 暑假里不用上学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不事先约好的话就见不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么一说也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还以为暑假里也能理所当然地和长谷同学见面
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用上课了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暑假不能经常见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 能见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才想来跟你说一声的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那暑假也要经常见面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们要在哪见面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织说要去见朋友 已经出门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还以为香织的朋友一定是指长谷同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了 错过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织妈妈还挺喜欢这种剧情的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了 你来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说是像平常一样见面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我也只能想到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}穿着便服进学校好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被老师发现会挨骂的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就不用勉强进来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我知道你一定会来 所以我才有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 藤宫同学 今天是星期一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早上看了日记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就想着 是长谷同学呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这么想着…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我很自然就认出你是长谷同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全没想过是初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这时候 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐 长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每过一周就会转回原点的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…认识长谷同学哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经几乎完全和我的齿轮紧紧咬合了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}星期一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说起来 为什么今天放学后还等我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们没说好要一起回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有东西要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊 今天是我生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是藤宫同学为什么会知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 饼干…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实是上周 桐生同学故意说得大声让我听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是为了把这个给我才特意在教室等我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了以防自己忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我写下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn经典中圆简\c&H000000&\blur0\bord0\frz6.814\pos(550,522)}长谷同学生日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学是怎么看待我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 我在问什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 刚刚的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.68,0:23:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我喜欢长谷同学喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下来的剧情一目了然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也很喜欢将吾和山岸同学对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也很喜欢数学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喜欢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Hu-…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Hu-？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朋友与海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
